{
  "id": "adv_main_03_07_03",
  "title": "BIG4編1章33話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_lesson-00-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――四人体制での初練習の日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The day of the first practice with four members",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_studio-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 1.4533333659
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "すぅ～……はぁぁ～……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whew… Sigh…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.2666668374,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "いざセンターに立つと、こんなにも緊張するのですわね\nですが、今の月ストの大黒柱は私、成宮すず！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m so nervous now that I’m actually standing in the center.\nBut the pillar of Moon Tempest now is me‚ Suzu Narumiya!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.4333333134,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃に恥じないどころか「うわー！　超えられたー！」\nと悔しがらせてみせますわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm not going to let Kotono down‚ in fact‚ I’ll make her regret it\nby making her say‚\"Wow! They’ve surpassed me!\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.0999992171,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "すずちゃん、その意気だよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's the spirit‚ Suzu-chan!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.4999995032,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "パフォーマンスが高まりそうな、程良い緊張具合ですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s the perfect amount of nervousness to boost your performance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.9999995032,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "さあ、いきますわよ！　1、2！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ here we go! 1‚ 2!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.0333328365,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "すずにゃん！　ステップが逆だよー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu-nyan! Your steps are reversed!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.1666664241,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "あぅ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ow.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.1333330908,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "（四人での練習はちょっと不安だったけど……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I was a little worried about practicing with four people…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.69999696,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "（今まで一緒に頑張ってきた仲間だし）\n（四人でも沢山話し合ってきたから、うまくやれてる）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(But we’ve always worked hard together‚)\n(and we’ve talked a lot even with four members‚ so we’re doing well.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.034795174,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "（琴乃ちゃん……見ててね）\n（私達、四人でも輝いてみせるから！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Kotono… Watch us.)\n(We’ll show you we can shine even with four members!)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.633329753,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 61.22675455
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅ、そろそろ休憩にしましょうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whew‚ shall we take a break?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.0333318193,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "（琴乃ちゃん、元気にしてるかな……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I wonder if Kotono is doing okay…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.2666636268,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ、この部分の振り付けなんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right‚ about the choreography for this part…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.8666636268,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　琴乃ちゃん、どの部分……って\nあ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm? Kotono‚ which part… she said\nAh…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.2999964196,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "ご、ごめん。ついクセで……\n……ほんとにごめん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-Sorry. It’s just a habit…\n…I’m really sorry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.7999964196,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "これくらい気にしませんわよ。ねえ、芽衣？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t worry about it. Right‚ Mei?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.5333302934,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "うん。渚ちゃんは琴乃ちゃんがだーい好きなんだから\nしょうがないしょうがない！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. Nagisa loves Kotono so much‚\nit can’t be helped!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.233329753,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "うん……ありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… Thanks.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.1666636268,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_comical-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 103.3999964196
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "渚ちゃん、元気出して？\nあ、みんなで琴乃ちゃんのお面をつけてみよっか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nagisa‚ cheer up!\nAh‚ why don’t we all wear Kotono masks?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.3999964196,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "ただの怪しい集団ですわよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We'd just be a suspicious group…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.5999969601,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "みんなが琴乃ちゃんのお面をかぶる……\n長瀬琴乃教、といったところでしょうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone wearing Kotono masks…\nI guess that would be the Kotono Nagase religion.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.2999964196,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "それいいね！\nグッズなら沢山あるから、布教なら任せて！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s a great idea!\nWe have a lot of merchandise‚ so leave the preaching to me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.033329753,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "……あー、いや、うん、なんでもない\nごめんね、すぐ興奮しちゃって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ah‚ no‚ um‚ never mind.\nSorry‚ I get excited easily…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.633329753,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pretty-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 131.7666636268
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫だよ。渚ちゃんが元気なのが一番大事だから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s okay. The most important thing is that you’re cheerful‚ Nagisa-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.7666636268,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "渚は、琴乃とは中学からの付き合いですものね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’ve been friends with Kotono since middle school‚ right‚ Nagisa?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.0333302934,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "それだけ長い間一緒にいたんですから\n考えてしまうのは自然なことですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’ve been together for so long‚\nit’s only natural that you’d think about her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.4999964196,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03-ngs011.m4a",
      "text": "……そう、だよね。みんな、ありがとう\n沙季ちゃん……ぎゅってしていい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yeah‚ you’re right. Thanks‚ everyone.\nSaki-chan… Can I hug you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.2666630863,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_07_03-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "いいですよ。甘えたい時は甘えて下さいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sure. Feel free to be spoiled when you want to be.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.3999969601,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
