      "text": "ここが今日のパーティー会場……三枝さんから\n話は聞いていたけど、ここまで規模が大きいとはな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So this is the party venue today… Saegusa-san\ntold me about it‚ but I didn’t know it would be this big.",
