      "text": "新生月ストを売り込むうってつけの機会だ\n俺も負けてられないな、まずは……ん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is the perfect opportunity to promote the reborn Moon Tempest.\nI can’t lose either‚ first… Hmm?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 188.7333897707,
      "sfxList": []
