      "text": "来夢が生配信で煽り過ぎて仕事先が減ったからでしょ？\nまぁ、私も別に悪いことをしたとは思ってないけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because you provoked too much on live stream‚ and we lost some work‚ right?\nWell‚ I don’t think we did anything wrong though.",
        "id": ""
